im curious why AVC still false flags this as incompatible with 1.3.1? the version file checks out... and I know I can delete the file to remove the false flag...but Id like to keep the file just in case an update gets pushed. since ya know...its a pretty major part of certain mods to function ![:)](//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_smiley.gif ":)")

